column5: Been trying to find one to go to this Saturday for Sue and I. Have I left it too late? Anyone know of one in the Kawartha's area? It would be much appreciated! I have tried searching on line but I'm not having a lot of success.
Might be late but you can contact them via phone or email: http://www.mcleanberryfarm.com/html/maplefest.html
April 8 & 9 Spring Tonic Maple Syrup Festival Tiffin Centre for ConservationNottawasaga Valley Conservation Area 10 min west of Barrie
The 2nd link has a bunch of places listed Cliff
There is one at the ganaraska forest centre on saturday.  S
Thank you so much guys, I think Sue and I are going to try to get out for a visit to one of them on Saturday! Really appreciate the help!
